  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nTo simplify the support of metrics in erigon we want to reduce the external dependencies down to the basic Prometheus go client.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\n1. Change the code in erigon\\metrics\\register.go to use prometheus metrics directly\r\n2. Re code any remaining victoria metrics dependencies\r\n3. Refactor the registration process (can probably be removed as you say)\r\n4. Move the metrics package to erigon-lib - so the changes cover all metrics.",
